Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.44,0:00:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard, Keita.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.87,0:00:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The reason your house\Nis so loud lately...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.88,0:00:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is because you're living\Nwith three pretty ladies.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.91,0:00:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,''Living with'' isn't the right way to put it.\NThey're candidates to be my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.59,0:00:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're women who may\Nbecome my dad's wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.09,0:00:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that. And the fact\Nyou're to choose one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.47,0:00:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up, Keita!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.02,0:00:46.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, Haruka Mikami, will run\Nas a mother candidate too!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.27,0:00:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
