Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.49,0:00:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.28,0:01:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter.\NI choose to, so it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.91,0:01:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not. You'd be\Na candidate to be my mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.75,0:01:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.92,0:01:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.47,0:01:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make you\Nspeechless with my charm!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.30,0:01:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,''Speechless''...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.00,0:01:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that you\Nwere in love with my dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.02,0:01:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.06,0:01:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious, Haruka?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.40,0:01:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Taguchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.69,0:01:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You showed up, Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.00,0:01:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruka, is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.34,0:01:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.52,0:01:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, wonderful, Haruka.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.47,0:01:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm welcome to the idea, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.45,0:01:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up, Keita. She's one\Nof the candidates now as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.41,0:01:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get a room ready\Nfor her quickly, understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.92,0:01:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm off to work now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.86,0:01:57.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.32,0:01:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You too, Haruka!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.12,0:02:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell did he come here for?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.27,0:02:11.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for dinner,\NMiss Sawagiri. It was great.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.19,0:02:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiyo, you're a good cook.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.52,0:02:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.52,0:02:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. Haruka just\Nlocked herself in her room.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.18,0:02:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, I'm sure she's tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.59,0:02:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,True, she was irritated at carrying\Nher luggage all by herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.03,0:02:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's like my dad. She won't\Nquit once she's gotten started.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.58,0:02:35.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure she'll get bored of it right\Naway, so please look after her till then.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.79,0:02:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, please leave it to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.98,0:02:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, where's Noriko?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.59,0:02:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, she was\Nwandering around before...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.31,0:02:45.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you call?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.48,0:02:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was having dinner with Haruka.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.28,0:02:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A sports player eats\Nso much. I was amazed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.64,0:02:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, you have good taste, Chiyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.55,0:03:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sometimes order takeout from\Nthis place too, but it's always good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.11,0:03:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takeout?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.35,0:03:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, they listen\Nto your requests pretty well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.53,0:03:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's perfect for people like us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.37,0:03:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Noriko...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.33,0:03:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What, Kazuho?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.80,0:03:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Sawagiri!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.72,0:03:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiyo, we don't care about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.24,0:03:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Did I do something again?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.07,0:03:29.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Sawagiri,\Nplease wait! Miss Sawagiri!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.16,0:03:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Sawagiri, I don't\Ncare about stuff like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.20,0:03:38.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I always got takeout\Nwhen I was alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.31,0:03:43.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry that I can't be of\Nany help! I'm completely no-good!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.74,0:03:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?\NYou're helping out a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.00,0:03:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't say such things.\NBecause of you, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.57,0:03:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A blackout?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.62,0:04:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's a blackout. Miss Sawagiri?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.10,0:04:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um, Keita, it's dark.\NI can't take the dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.75,0:04:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. It's just a blackout.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.21,0:04:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm scared.\NI'm scared of the dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.26,0:04:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you? I don't\Nlike being alone in the dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.38,0:04:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on. I'll come to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.33,0:04:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I stepped on something!{Repeat}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.91,0:04:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keita...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.99,0:04:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keita...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.63,0:04:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Chiyo, please don't\Ngrab hold of me like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.27,0:04:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keita... Keita... Keita...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.87,0:04:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Sawagiri, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.80,0:04:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.56,0:04:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keita...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.61,0:04:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't hurt yourself, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.63,0:04:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm bad with the dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.02,0:04:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared of it. I can't be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.62,0:04:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.\NI'm with you now after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.31,0:04:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Keita.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.38,0:05:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just glad I fell on the bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.93,0:05:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.75,0:05:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you just call me by my first name?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.48,0:05:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I? I'm very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.20,0:05:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't misunderstand.\NIt made me happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.75,0:05:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since coming here, I was the only\None you didn't call by first name.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.04,0:05:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't like it because I felt alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.74,0:05:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Keita, I want\Nto become closer to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.24,0:05:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Sawagiri, are you\Nsure you want to do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.94,0:05:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That won't do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.73,0:05:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That won't do.\NCall me by my first name.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.96,0:06:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Chiyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.57,0:06:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.84,0:06:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.10,0:06:44.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Keita...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.31,0:06:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.82,0:06:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait any longer...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.89,0:06:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Chiyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.38,0:06:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go. Huh? It's a little dark, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.77,0:06:59.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Keita, that's my anus.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.39,0:07:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.19,0:07:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.82,0:07:05.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keita, it's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.84,0:07:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be nice to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.76,0:07:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine now. Please put it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.70,0:07:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Miss Sawagiri?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.10,0:07:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so mean.{might need a exclamation mark} Use my first name.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.66,0:07:31.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Chiyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.04,0:08:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, don't tease it more than this! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.64,0:08:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that. Let me hear more\Nof your sweet voice, Miss Sawagiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.87,0:08:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say it again... Say my name, Keita!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.60,0:08:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you have to be\Nturned on a little more.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.52,0:08:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't be mean, Keita.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.19,0:08:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keita, I... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.98,0:08:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keita!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.43,0:08:51.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you're adorable, Chiyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.56,0:08:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please call me\Nby my first name again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.39,0:08:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.12,0:08:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. {Repeat}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.96,0:08:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.65,0:08:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.77,0:09:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.75,0:09:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keita...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.54,0:09:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll be going.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.25,0:09:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, have a good day, Chiyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.31,0:09:38.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have a good day!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.44,0:09:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keita, you called\NChiyo by her first name.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.22,0:09:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.91,0:09:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing did.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.25,0:09:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?\NIt seems kind of suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.39,0:09:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, it's weird only\Ncalling Chiyo by her last name.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.65,0:10:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you start today?\NThat's kind of weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.41,0:10:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen yesterday?{Repeat}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.44,0:10:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruka!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.44,0:10:04.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing really.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.33,0:10:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noriko.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.20,0:10:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After the lights went out, we just waited for them to come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.30,0:10:08.98,alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Those two are close, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.98,0:10:11.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a candidate for his mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.98,0:10:10.73,alt,,0000,0000,0000,,You're sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.73,0:10:11.92,alt,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.93,0:10:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't look that way to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.93,0:10:13.88,alt,,0000,0000,0000,,You're really sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.88,0:10:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.00,0:10:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what did you want to ask me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.99,0:10:25.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's not really\Nsomething I wanted to ask...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.00,0:10:31.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was wondering if you still\Nwanted to become Keita's mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.23,0:10:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I do. Why do you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.69,0:10:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure someone becoming his\Nmother should do something like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.06,0:10:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was wondering\Nwhat you thought about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.43,0:10:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is from the other\Nday when Keita and I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.74,0:10:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.69,0:10:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think\Nof my detective skills?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.90,0:10:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This wasn't like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.62,0:11:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're mistaken.\NI wasn't trying to do that...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.11,0:11:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I think it would be fine\Nif everyone became close.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.35,0:11:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazuho, the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.51,0:11:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Taguchi residence.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.57,0:11:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,J-Jinta? No, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.40,0:11:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.01,0:11:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.28,0:11:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.96,0:11:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm at the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.36,0:11:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to see it on my way home.
