Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.86,0:28:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although my footsteps \Ncreate a rhythm for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.78,0:28:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The image of me\Njumping deep in your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.20,0:28:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A halation{no idea what you want here.} reminiscent\Nof our promised place.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.47,0:28:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday the distance\Nbetween us will narrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.98,0:28:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l believe it, in that promised place.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.66,0:28:38.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that scenery\Nthat doesn't change...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.17,0:28:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...l looked up, and l can\Nhear your voice. l love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.55,0:27:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.83,0:29:30.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keita, you're passionate!
